data.title: Athletic Hall of Fame
data.meta_description: Athletic Hall of Fame - Notre Dame High School
data.text:
The next Athletic Hall of Fame will be held in of May 2026.

To nominate someone for the Class of 2026

please use the nomination form below.

Athletic Hall of Fame Nomination Form

To nominate a deserving athlete, coach or special contributor for the Notre Dame High School Athletic Hall of Fame, download the form and email it to alumni@ndnj.org.

Nominations are accepted at all times.
